    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Or you can just use this method in case you don't have StringUtils on hand:</p>\n\n<pre><code>public static String abbreviateString(String input, int maxLength) {\n    if (input.length() &lt;= maxLength) \n        return input;\n    else \n        return input.substring(0, maxLength-2) + \"..\";\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
