    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just in case you are looking for a way to trim and keep the LAST 10 characters of a string.</p>\n\n<pre><code>s = s.substring(Math.max(s.length(),10) - 10);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
