    "body" : "<p>// this is how you shorten the length of the string with ..\n// add following method to your class</p>\n<pre><code>private String abbreviate(String s){\n  if(s.length() &lt;= 10) return s;\n  return s.substring(0, 8) + &quot;..&quot; ;\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
